00:55:24.523 --> 00:55:28.532
Ali čak i kad odemo u
grad, to me ne zanima.

00:55:28.737 --> 00:55:31.802
Obveze su postale moje svetište.

00:55:35.435 --> 00:55:37.503
Sranje.

00:55:47.408 --> 00:55:49.419
Odlazi.

