01:11:13.848 --> 01:11:15.864
Chris!

01:11:25.029 --> 01:11:30.076
<i>Bok, Chris je. Nisam pored mobitela ili
ne želim razgovarati s tobom. Pozdrav.

01:11:33.982 --> 01:11:37.104
